snippet.textDisplay: The song Rabba sung by Tochi Raina will be a treat to all music lovers. Raina's devotion to music & the beautiful person he is from within comes across in his singing. The mysticism in his voice takes you to a different world & m looking forward to hear his combination with the music maestro A.R.Rehman. This song is a lovely mixture of melody & youthfulness with Jaggi's addition to it.
